            "synopsis" : {"type" : 23, "value" : "Dialogue covers the transition from the pretty illusion that is on the swamp to the fetid reality.\r\n\r\nTriggers when entering the area, or when the illusion is disrupted because of combat or because Ethel is dropping her disguise.\r\n\r\nThis means it may play for a Wildshaped player or even a summon or follower."}
